A small project in C using one Atmel ATiny85 to play a buzzer and controler 3 leds.

To compile this project you must have installed the WinAVR (http://winavr.sourceforge.net/)
The Code::Block will help you too (http://www.codeblocks.org/)

I have used the Pocket AVR Programmer (http://www.sparkfun.com/products/9825) to programmer the AVR.

 
Bellow the "schematic" of the circuit.

                 +-------------------+
                 |1 RST         VCC 8|
          --<R|--|2 PB3    PB2/INT0 7|
          --<G|--|3 PB4         PB1 6|--|B>--
                 |4 GND         PB0 5|--|-|--
                 +-------------------+
                       ATTiny85
